# 📝 To-Do List App

A simple and responsive To-Do List application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This app helps users organize tasks, track progress, and improve productivity through an intuitive user interface.

## 🚀 Features

- Add new tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Delete tasks
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile devices
- Clean and modern user interface
- Real-time task management without page reloads

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)

## 📂 Project Structure

```
todo-list/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── README.md
```

